    you can manually start <application>&app;</application> by doing:
  </para>
  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Command line</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Type <command>pk-application --verbose --no-daemon</command>,
          then press <keycap>Return</keycap>:
        </para>
